reviewText: As much as I like this video and many other this organization had produced, I have to tell you that this is a non-profit organization, meaning everybody working in the production and distribution does it for free, as well we do not charge any money for this, I wonder this store must bought it in a second hand store or something like that, but anyway they were mislead, this is a free of charge worldwide distributed item, get for free, or even downloaded for free from [...] and to the owners of this place that is selling the video, please be more careful when you buy something, The Watchtower Bible and Tract will not charge you for their Bible based publications, remember these are distributed worldwide FREE of charge. Thank you for taking this review in consideration.
